                Conférences
            </a></h1><ul class="universe-homepage-list"><li class="universe-homepage-list-element"><a class="universe-homepage-list-element-link" href="/dossiers/conferences-sur-la-philosophie"><span class="hot-topics-list-item-name">Philosophie</span></a></li><li class="universe-homepage-list-element"><a class="universe-homepage-list-element-link" href="/dossiers/conferences-sur-la-science"><span class="hot-topics-list-item-name">Science</span></a></li><li class="universe-homepage-list-element"><a class="universe-homepage-list-element-link" href="/dossiers/conferences-sur-la-psychologie"><span class="hot-topics-list-item-name">Psychologie</span></a></li><li class="universe-homepage-list-element"><a class="universe-homepage-list-element-link" href="/dossiers/conferences-sur-la-sexualite"><span class="hot-topics-list-item-name">Sexualité</span></a></li></ul><div class="universe-homepage-container row"><div class="teaser teaser-row
      teaser-article"><div class="teaser-image-container"><a href="/conferences/universite-bretagne-loire/comprendre-ce-qui-nous-attire" target="" class="teaser-visual" title="Pour mieux comprendre ce qui nous attire chez l’autre"><figure class="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject"><picture><source type="image/webp"
                                srcset="/img/article_default.png"data-dejavu-srcset="https://cdn.radiofrance.fr/s3/cruiser-production/2017/06/21294313-3bdc-4ab7-af98-4564c9f3cb5a/500x282_gettyimages-187797122.webp"class="dejavu"><img
