                                alt="Festival Cinéma en plein air 2020"                                class="dejavu " data-dejavu-src="https://cdn.radiofrance.fr/s3/cruiser-production/2020/07/afd27819-596b-4d0c-add6-774c6b96b087/500x282_affiche_40x60_plein_air_2020_-_wall-e.jpg"  width="500" height="282"/></picture></figure></a></div><div class="teaser-text"><div class="teaser-text-title"><a href="/evenement/cinema-en-plein-air-2020" target="" class="teaser-text" title="Festival Cinéma en plein air 2020"><span class="teaser-text-title-wrapper">Festival Cinéma en plein air 2020</span></a></div><a href="/evenement/cinema-en-plein-air-2020" target="" class="teaser-text" title="Festival Cinéma en plein air 2020"><div class="teaser-text-extratitle"><svg data-id="calendar" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="8" height="9" viewBox="0 0 8 9"><g fill="#80809D" fill-rule="evenodd"><path d="M0,9 L8,9 L8,2 L0,2 L0,9 Z M1.25687353,7.80647911 L6.74312647,7.80647911 L6.74312647,3.19352089 L1.25687353,3.19352089 L1.25687353,7.80647911 Z"/><polygon points="0 4 8 4 8 2 0 2"/><polygon points="1 2 2 2 2 0 1 0"/><polygon points="6 2 7 2 7 0 6 0"/></g></svg>

                            Du 17/07/2020 au 29/08/2020
                        </div></a><p class="teaser-text-chapo">
                                                    Une trentaine de grands films en plein air tout l&#039;été !

